      h3 Variables
      p
        | To highlight variables that should be replaced by real values, use the 
        code var
        |  tag.  This is often used as part of part of a table, to document parameters to an API or method:
      p
        code
          | GET /v1/polyfill
          var {minify}
          | .
          var {type}
      table
        tbody
          tr
            th Param
            th Where
            th Description
          tr
            td
              var minify
            td URL
            td
              | Whether to minify the result.  If omitted, output will include the full polyfill source, and a header comment with debug information about the user agent and which polyfills have been included in the bundle.  If set to 
